---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <main class="page-content">
    <h1>How We Do It: Our Approach & Our Promise</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">The following are our most important steps:</p>
    <nl><li>Ask.</li>
    <li>Listen.</li>
    <li>Analyze.</li>
    <li>Communicate.</li>
    <li>Solve.</li>
    <li>Communicate.</li>
    <li>Build.</li>
    <li>Communicate.</li>
    <li>Deliver.</li>
    <p>If you prefer, we can continue to maintain and update your new systems, or we can teach someone on your team the basics.</p>
    <p>Either way, we stand behind the quality and effectiveness of all our automations and integrations, so we guarantee satisfaction
    with everything we do: We work until you are delighted with your results.</p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 2rem;
    color: #eaeaea;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.85);
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }
</style> 